H0.text: What is the name of the lake formed in 1932 when the Zuider Zee was cut off from the North Sea by a dyke. Markermeer

H1.text: What is the name of the lake formed in 1932 when the Zuider Zee was cut off from the North Sea by a dyke. Wadden Sea

H2.text: What is the name of the lake formed in 1932 when the Zuider Zee was cut off from the North Sea by a dyke. Veluwemeer

H3.text: What is the name of the lake formed in 1932 when the Zuider Zee was cut off from the North Sea by a dyke. IJselmeer

A4.text: In 1932 the Zuiderzee was closed off by the Afsluitdijk... The Zuiderzee was no longer a sea inlet and was renamed IJsselmeer

A5.text: The IJsselmeer is a closed-off freshwater lake in the central Netherlands... which is also the namesake of the province of Overijssel
